briefTitle: An Evaluation of the Safety of CSF-1 in Presbyopic Subjects

eligibilityModule.eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Subjects must have presbyopia

Exclusion Criteria:

* Have any contraindications to the study medications or diagnoses that would confound the study data

outcomeMeasures.title: Number of Participants With Treatment Emergent Adverse Events.
outcomeMeasures.description: As this is a safety study, no efficacy outcome has been defined.
